{"tid":1524084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認清事實] 到而家仲有香港人幻想最終會有人出黎制衡/清算狗","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:21:18.000Z","uid":81236,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e5257a3bf0d943c0deab434efae8bfdc6654a6ec","tid":1524084,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"我想同你講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔會呀</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係覺得講句香港人加油，香港人就會勁啲？<br />\n你係唔係覺得講句黑狗還眼，就真係會有狗無左隻眼？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好再FF會有個聖人會出黎制衡/清算佢地</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地既暴行只會變成功績<br />\n<br />\n唔洗再諗咩共產黨將來清算佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地心裡覺得最終會有人制衡佢地就係一直停止唔再進步既最大障礙</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人繼續等待有人賜予你地公平正義吧<br />\n<br />\n呢一日你地一呢世都唔會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"20a9e72d9ce4bd0f037d11ab2fa79bf97b81702e","tid":1524084,"uid":81236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"佢地既暴行只會變成功績<br />\n<br />\n更加會比人歌頌千秋萬代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0bfe1708ba438588e2cff0b36d4ec5e9f23b57","tid":1524084,"uid":9390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"成功未變功績<br />\n失敗就等清算<br />\n不過宜家睇落佢地成功既機率大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ce651c9189c1b3b9f3ff5467d8682bf8f62a41","tid":1524084,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce0bfe1708ba438588e2cff0b36d4ec5e9f23b57","tid":